%% Matrix guard — rozpor fyzické matice vs logická deska
%%{init: {'theme':'dark','themeVariables':{'fontFamily':'system-ui,sans-serif','clusterBkg':'#0f172a','clusterBorder':'#334155','lineColor':'#94a3b8','primaryTextColor':'#f1f5f9','edgeLabelBackground':'#1e293b','titleColor':'#f8fafc'}}}%%
flowchart TD
  MT[matrix_task: matrix_detect_moves] --> M[sestavil lifted/dropped masky 64 polí]
  M --> SEND[matrix_send_guard_command → GAME_CMD_MATRIX_GUARD]
  SEND --> GQ[(game_command_queue)]
  GQ --> PC[game_process_commands]
  PC --> H[game_handle_matrix_guard_command]

  H --> A{action == 0?}
  A -->|ano| CLR[matrix_guard_pause_state vypnout · LED clear · game_highlight_movable_pieces]
  A -->|ne| CON{game_matrix_guard_mode_conflict_active?}

  CON -->|ano| IGN[režim tutorial/puzzle/promo/rošáda/resignation/… — guard ignorován · matrix_abort_ambiguous_guard_baseline]
  CON -->|ne| ACT[active=true · uložit masky · conflict_count]
  ACT --> FZ[vyčistit piece_lifted / capture_in_progress]
  FZ --> LED[game_render_matrix_guard_leds — logika vs matrix_get_state]

  LED --> LEG[legenda: žlutá/modrá = figurka v logice · oranžová = jen senzor · bílá = chybí podle logiky]
